         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">14/9/65. ¶ Sir George. ¶  ¶ Your Excellency all along has evinced such a friendly interest in the promotion of all that is good, as to encourage me to solicit your friendly aid in obtaining for some m...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">65.09.14</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To George Grey</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Auckland Public Library, Grey Papers, GL M50(5)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS is written 'Ladies' Leichardt (<seg style="font-style: italic; ">sic</seg>) Search Committee' letterhead paper </p>
               </note>14/9/65.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir George.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your Excellency all along has evinced such a friendly interest in the promotion of all that is good, as to encourage me to solicit your friendly aid in obtaining for some mediterranean Gardens a gift out of your flora.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am anxious to decorate the gardens of South Europe and a few other parts of the globe with groves of New Zealand <name key="Areca">Areca</name> Palms and with our hardy Australian <name key="Corypha">Corypha</name> &amp; <name key="Seaforthia">Seaforthia</name>. I have a large supply of fresh seeds of the two latter palms secured, but want yet a quantity of fresh well matured <name key="Areca">Areca</name> seeds from your Islands. If it was possible to secure them through your Excellencys instrumentality I should feel so profoundly obliged, and if any of the New Zealand Garden establishments would secure the supply, I should most gladly reciprocate [with] whatever is here within my reach.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See also M to G. Grey, 27 November 1865.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>During the dreadful war period in your Excellencys territory<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Second Maori Wars, 1861-71.</p>
               </note> the spirit of my horticultural friends has sunk &amp; I really do not know any one to whom I could apply. Were it otherwise I should not have ventured to trifle with your Excellencys time in the manner I have done.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With profound veneration</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
